cc sn phm dch v ca Cng ty C phn Cng Ngh Qi, Khi Qu khch truy cp
vo website https://tracuu.qi.com.vn/ (sau y gi l "QI") ca chng ti, c ngha
l qu khch ng vi cc iu khon s dng di y.
Nhm m bo quyn li ca khch hng v tun th quy nh ca php lut, QI
thng xuyn c cp nht, b sung cc ni dung trong iu khon s dng ny.
Cc thay i c hiu lc ngay khi c ng ti cng khai trn QI. Khi qu khch
tip tc s dng QI, sau khi cc thay i v Quy nh v iu kin c ng ti, c
ngha l qu khch chp nhn vi nhng thay i . Qu khch vui lng kim tra
thng xuyn cp nht nhng thay i ca chng ti.

II/ Chnh sch, thi gian cam kt s dng v hon tr thit b QI
QI cung cp v gi quyn s hu ton b vt t, thit b (dy thu bao, u ni, cp LAN,
ngoi tr phn vt t thit b m khch hng mua t nh mng) phc v kt ni ng truyn
dn t tp im n im kt ni cui cng ca mng l a im s dng dch v Internet ca
Khch hng. Cc vt t, thit b ny l thuc quyn s hu ca QI ton quyn thu hi khi Khch
hng ngng s dng dch v.
Trng hp Khch hng s dng dch v Internet QI v mun tm ngng/chm dt hp ng
trc Thi hn cam kt quy nh ti Hp ng th Khch hng ng s khng c hon li s
tin thanh ton cn d v hon tr cho QI cc Thit b u cui v cc thit b, vt t khc thuc
s hu ca QI

VIII. Chnh sch bo hnh, bo tr ca QI
a. Th tc thc hin bo hnh
1.1. i vi Modem wifi/Converter:
Modem/Converter l thit b m QI cung cp cho Khch hng mn xuyn sut trong qu trnh
s dng dch v theo Hp ng ; Qi thc hin bo hnh thit b Modem/Converter trong sut
qu trnh s dng dch v ca Khch hng m bo vic cung cp dch v.
Trng hp Khch hng thay i, nng cp thit b, chnh sch bo hnh i vi thit b c
thay i nng cp s p dng theo chnh sch ca QI ty tng thi im.
m bo quyn li khch hng khi s dng thit b, Khch hng cn tun th cc quy nh v
s dng dch v, trnh cc s kin gy h hng i vi thit b nh va p, nc vo, s dng
sai hng dn, quy cch ca sn phm
Trng hp thit b h hng do li ca Khch hng s bi thng gi tr ca thit b theo quy
nh QI ti thi im .
2.1. Thi gian bo tr
H tr trong vng t 2 gi - 4 gi k t thi im nhn c yu cu hoc xy ra s kin hoc
theo k hoch.
IX. Chnh sch hy/ tm ngng s dng v hon tin

sinh (nu c).
b. Trng hp hy hp ng sau khi s dng
i vi Khch hng tr sau: Khch hng phi thanh ton cc khon n cc (nu c) v cc
khon tin tng ng vi thi gian s dng tnh n ngy chm dt/ tm ngng;
i vi Khch hng tr trc: Khch hng phi thanh ton cc khon tin tng ng vi thi
gian s dng tnh n ngy chm dt;

dch v s c thu hi.
Trng hp thit b h hng do li ca Khch hng s bi thng gi tr ca thit b theo quy
nh QI ti thi im .
